OL,3,CRailway station access won't be
OL,4,Ccompleted until campaigner is old man
OL,6,FITV Granada Reports correspondent Andy
OL,7,FBonner spoke to Nathaniel Yates about
OL,8,Fhis campaign.
OL,10,FA campaigner has told ITV News he will
OL,11,Fbe an old man before a programme to
OL,12,Fimprove accessibility at railway
OL,13,Fstations is completed.
OL,15,FNathaniel Yates, 31, who has cerebral
OL,16,Fpalsy, has been calling for better
OL,17,Faccess since he fell on stairs at his
OL,18,Flocal station in Greater Manchester in
OL,19,F2013.
