OL,3,CRailway station access won't be
OL,4,Ccompleted until campaigner is old man
OL,6,FHe said when he returned five years
OL,7,Flater, he realised that nothing had
OL,8,Fchanged.
OL,10,FHowever, he has since learned that
OL,11,Fhalf of all stations in the city
OL,12,Fregion don't have step-free access.
OL,14,FThe local transport authority is
OL,15,Fprioritising stations to apply for
OL,16,Ffunding to make improvements, but
OL,17,FNathaniel said it would be 2070 before
OL,18,Fall stations would be fully accessible
OL,19,Fat the current rate.
