OL,3,CRailway station access won't be
OL,4,Ccompleted until campaigner is old man
OL,6,F"Maybe it will be in my lifetime," he
OL,7,Fsaid. "I may be an old man before
OL,8,Fthen!"
OL,10,FTransport for Greater Manchester
OL,11,F(TfGM) says around 45% of railway
OL,12,Fstations have step-free access. A
OL,13,Ffurther 14% have steep ramps which are
OL,14,Fonly partially accessible.
OL,16,FNathaniel has been campaigning for
OL,17,Fimprovements at Levenshulme station,
OL,18,Fwhere the platforms are at the top of
OL,19,Ftwo flights of steps.
