OL,3,CRailway station access won't be
OL,4,Ccompleted until campaigner is old man
OL,6,FIt has now been identified as the top
OL,7,Fpriority station and TfGM says it is
OL,8,Fexploring funding opportunities.
OL,10,FSimon Elliott, Head of Rail at TfGM,
OL,11,Fsaid: "Improving rail station
OL,12,Faccessibility is a key priority for
OL,13,Fthe city region and over the last few
OL,14,Fyears Transport for Greater Manchester
OL,15,Fhas been working with Northern,
OL,16,FNetwork Rail and other partners and
OL,17,Fstakeholders to make our railways as
OL,18,Faccessible as possible.
OL,26,@sD@GOU
