OL,3,CRailway station access won't be
OL,4,Ccompleted until campaigner is old man
OL,6,F"We have reviewed all stations across
OL,7,Fthe city-region to identify those most
OL,8,Fin need of step free access to develop
OL,9,Fa prioritised list which is used to
OL,10,Fdetermine where we focus funding as it
OL,11,Fbecomes available.
OL,13,F"Funding has been secured to make 10
OL,14,Fpriority stations step free, two of
OL,15,Fwhich ` Daisy Hill and Irlam ` are
OL,16,Fcurrently in construction, and the
OL,17,Fothers in various stages of design."
OL,26,@uD@AOU
