OL,3,CRailway station access won't be
OL,4,Ccompleted until campaigner is old man
OL,6,F"For people to fully access all the
OL,7,Fservices they need, there needs to be
OL,8,Fstep-free access across the borough."
OL,10,FNathaniel added, "Everybody should
OL,11,Fhave the right to use the trains.
OL,12,FAccess should be for all."
